snippet: In the span of a few hours Sunday, the Kansas City Chiefs went from controlling the AFC West and taking care of a playoff spot to watching the Oakland Raiders take everything instead....
lead_paragraph: In the span of a few hours Sunday, the Kansas City Chiefs went from controlling the AFC West and taking care of a playoff spot to watching the Oakland Raiders take everything instead.

headline.main: Chiefs Go From Clinching Playoffs to Chasing Oakland in West
headline.print_headline: Chiefs Go From Clinching Playoffs to Chasing Oakland in West
